txt.en: 'The tents have been fully prepared and made ready for the people of the Entwash Vale to come and join your town as inhabitants and not just visitors. They will add a breath of fresh air and new life to Hytbold. Those coming are a varied sort: women, children, warriors, and craftsmen. All have been displaced by the Enemy, and all will now call this place home.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
